{
  "stem": "18865.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I received the answer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I received a letter that I was accepted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in April of 1939, I left Krefeld.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Left everyone, everything behind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with 11 suitcases and a bicycle, I went first to Holland, and from there to Rotterdam, and from Rotterdam to England.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there I was picked up by the-- oh, well, first I have to explain how I got out with a-- a certificate that said born in 1920 and a passport that said born in 1921.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the fear that I-- that would be discovered was great.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was very fortunate, because we lived so close to the Dutch border that by the time we-- we arrived in Holland, in Venlo, we-- the-- the official person who-- who the-- controls-- I mean, checks all the-- the documents, was in the department right next to me.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I heard his voice, and shortly-- and I was-- was very scary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I heard outside yelling, [SPEAKING GERMAN], that the Dutch couldn't wait to get these Germans off the train.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they never came to my-- to my compartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was safe there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But then came the danger of England.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If they check it--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I then-- I then went to visit my father in prison.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in prison in Krefeld.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had to tell them there what I did and that I was accepted.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said goodbye.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was very difficult, one of the hardest things I ever did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He felt totally unable to be of any support to his family, to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And was equally difficult, then, to say goodbye to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went to see my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was still so young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was all so-- everything came so very fast.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
